    <div id="untitled-region-1" class="first editable">
     <h3>
      About Keepsakes, Pitlochry, Scotland
     </h3>
     <p>
      <strong>
       Keepsakes
      </strong>
      owners, David Litterick and Lynda Hudda have been
in retail for almost 20 years having owned a gift shop in the Western
Isles...
     </p>
     <p>
      After moving back to the mainland, they began looking for a new business and
decided Keepsakes was just what they were looking for. They took over the
business in May 2013.
     </p>
     <p>
      They have continued to maintain the high level of service and offer the wide
range of quality gifts and jewellery that their customers have come to
expect.
     </p>
     <p>
      David and Lynda look forward to welcoming both new and existing customers to
Keepsakes.
     </p>
    </div>
